{"tid":1012202,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係好明點解猁狗可以咁雙重標準","createTime":"2019-02-07T11:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T12:51:55.000Z","uid":201601,"like":111,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea681e0f87038a7bcbc583ad79c9d623d65b6a0","tid":1012202,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:42:18.000Z","msg":"今季英超嗰啲就唔講啦，黑哨到咁都可以屌返人轉頭，好似啱啱嗰場咁，明明自己越位入波，高daddy都可以屌返個球證下半場偏袒對面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住連登入面嗰班傻閪猁迷成春日喺度屌古天樂25，但我記得之前猁非法接觸van dijk搞到畀修咸頓告，結果玩到猁搞埋哂啲咩道歉聲明，話咩唔會再有興趣去買佢，猁狗係咪冇撚咗件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999b23bc8d41d8c7d9cb9dc1a5025f424aadf7b8","tid":1012202,"uid":201601,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"補返個聲明張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/02HTThh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F02HTThh.png&h=4e92713e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"167aff2bbb731f8da2eb62ec826a19646ac7873b","tid":1012202,"uid":201601,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:43:34.000Z","msg":"不服來辯"},{"pid":"51d9caa8da50cb10f9e948c30b7e121ada374466","tid":1012202,"uid":201601,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T11:46:17.000Z","msg":"話咁快已經有隻猁狗靜靜雞咁畀咗負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e845fff03f6729edfa00a67a3aba0b13d2355ab","tid":1012202,"uid":3244,"like":16,